Nemesis Enforcer/Scattershot/The Oblitercons/Jaws/Punch:



Nemesis Enforcer rested uncomfortably and painfully in a CR chamber.  

Scattershot lay in a CR tank, letting the liquid repair him, having already 
put Serpentor's head somewhere safe on the island.  

All the Oblitercons were in CR chambers, all in the original Alliance base.

===

Jaws continued with his underwater patrol, having taken no notice of any of 
the recently arriving Alliance members. 

---

Punch still lay asleep on his recharge bed, his shift not for a long time.
